::Prowl::

Prowl advances alongside Epyon, his energy staff in his hand. He 
wouldn't let Megatron kill his mate, but he wouldn't interfere 
either. Hearing a yell behind him, he turns around, two cyclone shots 
nearly hitting him. He flies into the air and fires two missiles from 
his wings at Menasor, noticing that Megatron had ordered a retreat.

-That coward,- he thinks to Iron Raptor, -Oh well, you would have 
beaten him, love.-
